Today on The Breakfast Club we are joined by friend to the show, icon, and sports commentator, Stephen A. Smith! Later during the Rumor Report we talk about Latto's latest cypher and Angela takes on callers advice during Ask Yee. Charlamagne gives us todays Donkey of The Day and Positive Note
